    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out under MRL 2 requirements. CFD predictions of the relative hemolysis index satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device across all 5 flow-speed combinations. The overall credibility evidence supports use of the CFD model for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
